uests choose the needed property quickly and easily.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_02.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-710936\\\" \\/>Accommodation Booking System<\\/h3>\\r\\nCiestra Rental Property WordPress theme is powered by our custom plugin - the popular <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\" title=\\\"WordPress reservation\\\">WordPress reservation<\\/a> system. It\\u2019s a built-in powerhouse for all your bookings, properties directory, seasonal prices, rates, taxes and fees management and the whole array of tools for lodging business.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe real-time search availability form enables guests to automatically search through all rentals and book online instantly or leave a booking request.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe premium MotoPress Hotel Booking plugin is included for free!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_03.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-710937\\\" \\/>Beautiful Galleries & Slideshows<\\/h3>\\r\\nThis real estate WordPress theme gives you a lot of space for images and calls-to-action. Keep your website up-to-date with what travellers want: provide helpful info about nearby bars and attractions, services, landscapes, events and more.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe WordPress rental theme is equipped with unique, easily editable Elementor builder content modules for providing an unforgettable pre-vacation experience for your guests.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_04.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-710938\\\" \\/>Sync Bookings to OTAs like Airbnb<\\/h3>\\r\\nDon\\u2019t miss on other popular listing websites! Rent out the properties elsewhere and sync bookings to your independent website built with Ciestra Rental theme.\\r\\n\\r\\nThanks to the iCal support, the reservation system is able to automatically sync your hotel bookings to external OTAs without overbooking (make sure the medium platform supports iCal). Forget about channel managers and third-party commissions!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_05.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-710939\\\" \\/>Prepayment or Pay at the Property<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou are free to enable guests to pay online safely a full or deposit price (fixed \\/ percentage) or charge them after arrival.\\r\\n\\r\\nThere are several out-of-the-box payment gateways you can enable: PayPal, 2Checkout, Stripe, Braintree and Beanstream\\/Bambora. Need more methods? Purchase our Pro <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\" title=\\\"WooCommerce Payments add-on\\\">WooCommerce Payments add-on<\\/a> to add a desirable gateway without coding.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_06.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-710940\\\" \\/>Weekly and Monthly Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nNeed to set up a complex & dynamic pricing system? Simple. Discount your hotel rooms or other resort accommodations automatically for a longer stay with weekly, monthly or other customizable rates. Designate price variables based on the room\\u2019s capacity.\\r\\n\\r\\nWith the integrated WordPress Hotel Booking plugin, you can set any number of days and apply any per-night price for the set stay-in duration and the number of guests.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_07.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-710941\\\" \\/>Simple & Advanced Booking Rules<\\/h3>\\r\\nFor each property and season you can set up min \\/ max days to stay, available check-in and check-out dates, block chosen units for a certain period of time and more.\\r\\n\\r\\nAvailability calendars of all properties will display available and unavailable days in real time according to your rules.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_08.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-710942\\\" \\/>Free & Paid Bookable Extras<\\/h3>\\r\\nAn easy way to entice guests to buy more extras along with the property bookings: offer extra packages and services and eventually find a bigger sum in every check! They can be added to cart on the checkout page.\\r\\n\\r\\nSet the price per accommodation \\/ guest; once or per night. You can also offer free services that must be booked in advance.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_09.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-710943\\\" \\/>Instagram Gallery<\\/h3>\\r\\nInstagram is a perfect medium for hotels and vacation rentals to engage with guests and project their story.\\r\\n\\r\\nWith Ciestra, you can focus on image storytelling with a lightweight and beautiful Instagram gallery that automatically displays a feed of your latest Instagram uploads. Generate leads easily and turn them into clients.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/ciestra_10.png\\\"