h to be used by agencies that offer multiple apartments for rent, condos or home rentals.\\r\\n\\r\\nThanks to the property management plugin built in, you are able to display and rent out online any number of properties.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-703309\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_galleries_slideshows.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Custom Crafted Galleries and Slideshows<\\/h3>\\r\\nBring an unforgettable pre-vacation experience to your prospective tenants by employing pre-made content modules. Stunning yet lightweight image galleries, unique slideshow of amenities and services, capacity counters and more tools are at your disposal.\\r\\n\\r\\nProfessionally showcase all details about your rental unit and market it like a pro.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703308 alignright\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_wp_booking_system_for_rental_units.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_wp_booking_system_for_rental_units\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>WordPress Booking System for Rental Units<\\/h3>\\r\\nAquentro is packaged with a top-rated <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">WordPress booking plugin<\\/a> for hotels, vacation rentals and other types of rental properties. This plugin consolidates an all-around property management system (rental units, inventory, categorized amenities and services, bed types, etc.), reservation system integrated with the payment gateways, availability calendars, OTAs channel manager and more.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe premium MotoPress Hotel Booking plugin is <strong>included for free.<\\/strong>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703343 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_sync_bookings_with_airbnb_and_other_otas.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_sync_bookings_with_airbnb_and_other_otas\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Sync Bookings with Airbnb and Other OTAs<\\/h3>\\r\\nListing your property elsewhere? It\\u2019s easy to synchronize all bookings coming through external online travel agents with direct website bookings.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf an OTA you use supports iCal file format, you\\u2019ll be able to sync its bookings with direct website reservations (near real time auto sync). Avoid overbooking without extra commissions and channel managers!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703306 alignright\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_prepaid_online_bookings_or_charge_upon_arrival.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_prepaid_online_bookings_or_charge_upon_arrival\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Prepaid Online Bookings or Charge upon Arrival<\\/h3>\\r\\nWant to accept payments and confirm bookings automatically? You can do it easily with built-in payment gateways: PayPal, 2Checkout, Stripe, Braintree and Beanstream\\/Bambora.\\r\\n\\r\\nGuests pay online a full or deposit price (fixed \\/ percentage) or can be charged only after arrival. Optionally disable booking functionality and simply feature your rentals.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you need more region-specific gateways, you can purchase our custom <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\">WooCommerce Payments add-on<\\/a>.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703305 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_flexible_booking_rules.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_flexible_booking_rules\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Flexible Booking Rules<\\/h3>\\r\\nSet min \\/ max days to stay, available check-in and check-out dates for all rentals at once, accommodations individually or seasons. Totally block chosen units for a certain period of time.\\r\\n\\r\\nAvailability calendars of the property will display available and unavailable days in real time according to your rules.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703304 alignright\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_weekly_monthly_rates.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_weekly_monthly_rates\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Weekly and Monthly Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nDo you want to designate different price points based on the length of stay? It\\u2019s simple to discount your rental units automatically for a longer stay with weekly, monthly or other customizable rates.\\r\\n\\r\\nWith the integrated Hotel Booking plugin, you can set any number of days and apply any per-night price for the set stay-in duration.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703303 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_free_paid_extra_services.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_free_paid_extra_services\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Free or Paid Extra Services<\\/h3>\\r\\nSell extra services and packages (set the price per accommodation \\/ guest; once or per night) or offer them for free.\\r\\n\\r\\nGuests will be able to view all available services for the chosen accommodation and add them to the cart.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703302 alignright\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_one_click_demo_data_import.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_one_click_demo_data_import\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>One-Click Demo Data Import<\\/h3>\\r\\nThis single property website template is absolutely easy on customization thanks to dummy data that you can import in one click and get started in minutes.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe data importer is packed with the theme allowing you to replace sample info with your custom content with no hassle.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-703301 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_built_with_jetpack_and_elementor.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"aquentro_built_with_jetpack_and_elementor\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Built with Jetpack and Elementor<\\/h3>\\r\\nTo help you customize this single property WordPress theme with extremely user-friendly, tried &amp; trusted tools, we\\u2019ve included top popular WordPress plugins.\\r\\n\\r\\nEnjoy Elementor plugin for visual content editing and Jetpack for tons of useful cogs like galleries, testimonials widget, performance optimization and more.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>More features of the Aquentro Single Property WordPress theme:<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Responsive and Retina ready design<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Delicate typography<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Extremely fast-loading theme<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Widgets created specifically for Elementor<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Social media integration<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Jetpack Testimonials widget<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Jetpack Contact form<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Pre-built pages for different purposes (About property, Contact Us, Activities, etc.)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Integration with native WordPress functionality (parent and child pages)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Stunning blog layout (single post with and without sidebar)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Two widget areas (footer and front page top)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Full-width and grid page templates<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Customizable menus<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>SVG support<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>HTML5 &amp; CSS3 &amp; latest WP standards<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>SEO Optimized markup<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Structured Data markup<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Clean source code<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Priority support: ticket system, live chat and email<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Fully documented.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>More features of the built-in WordPress reservation system:<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Premium MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">Hotel Booking<\\/a> plugin included for free<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Suitable for unlimited rentals<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Availability calendars for rentals<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Real-time search availability form<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Property rates and seasonal pricing<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>No extra commissions on bookings<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Price variables based on the number of people<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Dedicated taxes and fees management<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Booking confirmation by admin, tenant or upon payment<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Personalized discount coupons<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Multiple currencies<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Handy bookings management for vacation rental owners and managers<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Booking email notifications for admin and customer<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Optional property recommendation based on a number of guests<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Customizable shortcodes<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Translated into 14 languages<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\">WooCommerce Payments<\\/a> add-on to enable region-specific gateways (optional premium add-on; not included into the theme).<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Aquentro is an urban-style single property WordPress theme for all types of units from high-end luxury apartments to hotels. The main theme demo is optimized a single property for rent, but thanks to the premium WordPress reservation plugin integrated for free, it can be used for unlimited properties. The theme is extremely lightweight and vibrant, easy on customization and powerful.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/aquentro_theme_1200x3000.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                 