ee!).\\r\\n\\r\\nFeature all details about a property and its apartments: amenities, photos, descriptions, size, view, bed types, sleeps, availability, extra services, etc. Enable a real-time search availability form and a WordPress booking calendar for properties.\\r\\n<h3>Sync Bookings with Airbnb and Other OTAs<\\/h3>\\r\\nRent out directly and through agencies - avoid overbooking without extra commissions and channel managers! Synchronize all bookings submitted on your vacation rental WordPress website with those from OTAs like Airbnb with the built-in reservation plugin.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe system supports automatic WordPress iCal sync enabling you to exchange booking calendars with the popular rental property agencies where your accommodation is listed (make sure the former supports iCal).\\r\\n<h3>Prepaid Online Bookings or Charge upon Arrival<\\/h3>\\r\\nProcess online payments via built-in payment gateways and increase your international travelers audience: PayPal, 2Checkout, Stripe, Braintree, Beanstream\\/Bambora, etc. The system sends money straight to your chosen accounts!\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you need to use more local gateways, add them with our custom <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\">WooCommerce Payments<\\/a> addon.\\r\\n\\r\\nGuests can pay online a full \\/ deposit price or can be charged only after arrival. Optionally disable a booking functionality and simply feature your rentals.\\r\\n<h3>Flexible Booking Rules<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe PMS allows you to set min \\/ max days to stay and available check-in and check-out dates for all rentals at once, accommodations individually or seasons.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also make certain accommodations unavailable for a chosen period of time (set not check-in, not check-out or not stay-in rules). Optionally set different rates by setting price variables based on a number of guests.\\r\\n<h3>Booking Confirmation Modes<\\/h3>\\r\\nConfirm property bookings automatically or manually, with or without a payment:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>by guest via email (confirmation link)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>by admin manually (confirmation link)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>by payment (full or deposit).<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nNot confirmed bookings during a set period of time become abandoned making them available for further reservation.\\r\\n<h3>Seasonal Pricing and Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe high-season weeks demand the higher prices. Set different prices for low and high seasons, weekends, or whatever period you want.\\r\\n\\r\\nBased on a number of advantages offered for a specific accommodation, you can set different prices for the same accommodation type \\u2013 rates (e.g. non-refundable double room rate, refundable double room rate, etc).\\r\\n<h3>Weekly and Monthly Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou can set any unit \\/ apartment price depending on a season (any term). To create different price points based on the length of stay within the season, you can add weekly, monthly or other customizable rates. Set any number of days and apply a needed per-night price for the set stay-in duration.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe system will automatically discount the properties according to your rate rules. A better per-night rate for a longer stay will help you stay competitive in the industry!\\r\\n<h3>Free or Paid Extra Services<\\/h3>\\r\\nOffer bookable extra services or packages along with the accommodation.\\r\\n\\r\\nCharge per accommodation or per person, one time or per night. Guests can add any preferable service to the cart when making a booking. You may easily feature all available services on the website with details.\\r\\n<h3>Taxes and Fees<\\/h3>\\r\\nCollect and file mandatory fees, accommodation taxes, service taxes and fee taxes. Always have complete and correct pricing information on all accommodation charges.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe guests will be able to see the detailed summary of charges before confirming a booking. All payment info of each booking is stored in the admin dashboard for easier accounting.\\r\\n<h3>Discount Coupons<\\/h3>\\r\\nManually create personalized discount coupons for loyal guests or for using in promo campaigns!\\r\\n\\r\\nYou\\u2019ll be able to set a discount amount, an expiration date, select applicable accommodation types, set check-in and check-out dates, min and max days to stay and apply other settings. For the automatic discounts based on the length of stay, you\\u2019ll need to configure property rates.\\r\\n<h3>One-Click Demo Data Import<\\/h3>\\r\\nImport sample data to the WordPress theme in one click and get your vacation rental website just like on the demo!\\r\\n\\r\\nThe data importer is packed with the theme, so you\\u2019ll be able to replace sample data with your custom content without any hassle.\\r\\n<h3>Native Integration with WordPress<\\/h3>\\r\\nThis WordPress vacation rental theme is seamlessly integrated with a native WordPress functionality making it really lightweight in terms of performance.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe did no overload this real estate WordPress theme with redundant plugins providing only the booking powerhouse consistent with a real lodging business. The theme customization is also a breeze, you won\\u2019t lose your content even if you switch the theme.\\r\\n<h3>Multiple Page Templates<\\/h3>\\r\\nGive your holiday rental WordPress website a needed look and feel with minimalistic or complex layouts. The WordPress vacation rental theme comes with different layout options: left sidebar, right sidebar, without sidebar, front page, front page without sidebar, grid left sidebar and grid without sidebar.\\r\\n<h3>Layouts for Accommodation Types<\\/h3>\\r\\nBased on the number of your rentals, you can choose the best way to display them on your website: a standard, list or grid.\\r\\n<h3>Testimonials<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou may add and customize the look of the guest reviews with the Testimonials widget powered by the professional Jetpack WordPress plugin.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe plugin allows to upload the photos of guests and add their reviews to display them beautifully on your website.\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<h2>More features of Mountainview Vacation Rental WordPress theme:<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Breadcrumbs for a handy navigation<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>WPML support for multilingual websites<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Lightweight and fast-loading theme<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>2 post layouts (left sidebar and without sidebar) independent from the main layout<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Translation ready<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Fully customizable header and footer menus<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Social integration<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>HTML5 &amp; CSS3 &amp; latest WP standards<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>SEO Optimized markup<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Structured Data markup<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Clean source code<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Priority support: ticket system, live chat and email<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Fully documented.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<h2>More features of the built-in WordPress reservation system:<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Admin and guest email notifications<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Image galleries of accommodations<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Multiple accommodations booking by one guest<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Translated into 14 languages<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>WordPress booking calendar<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Easy to use for vacation rental owners and managers<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Optional accommodation recommendation based on a number of guests<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Cancellation policy (connected to cancellation email notifications)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Admin calendar of bookings with the user-friendly interface and filters<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Painless booking process for guests<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Full or deposit payments (percentage or flat rate) or payments after arrival<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\">WooCommerce Payments add-on<\\/a> to go beyond default payment gateways. <strong>[optional premium add-on; not included into the theme]<\\/strong>.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Mountainview Vacation Rental WordPress theme is a lightweight, elegant and powerful theme for rental property owners. Rent out your cabin, chalet, villa or any other holiday home with a built-in dedicated property reservation WordPress plugin. Customize the theme without restrictions, connect rentals with external travel agents via iCalendar, set custom rates for peak seasons, process secure online bookings without any commission and so much more.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/07\\/mountainview-theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 844,\n                        \"name\": \"Hotel and Property Rental WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"hotel-rental-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 844,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Vacation rental WordPress themes and Hotel themes with the built-in WordPress Hotel Booking plugin by MotoPress included for free.\\r\\n\\r\\nThese property rental WordPress themes will definitely help you display the facilities and advantages of your single property website, small family hotel, elite boutique, hostel or cosy apartment for rent. Each template is beautifully designed, well-structured and equipped with easy booking tool - WordPress Booking plugin. \\r\\n\\r\\nMotoPress WordPress reservation plugin offers easy property management system, an iCal channel manager for OTAs, built-in payment gateways, offline and online payments, availability calendar, extra services, booking calendar, custom rates, seasonal pricing, taxes & fees, discount coupons and much more.\\r\\n\\r\\nUse this perfect combo of Hotel Booking Plugin and WordPress real estate theme and build your successful business with MotoPress\\r\\n\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 7,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"59.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 687897,\n                \"slug\": \"alpenhouse\",\n                \"title\": \"Alpenhouse\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-06-12 12:46:08\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-09-18 13:48:20\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=687897\",\n                \"content\": \"<h2 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Hotel Booking WordPress Theme Highlights<\\/h2>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689759\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_accommodation_reservation_system.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress vacation rental theme\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Property Reservation System<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreate a directory of your accommodations and enable direct reservations with this hotel booking WordPress theme and our <strong>premium <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">WordPress booking plugin<\\/a> (included for free!).<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nRent out a guest house bookable by the room or multiple houses.\\r\\n\\r\\nFeature all details about a property and its rooms: amenities, photos, descriptions, size, bed types, sleeps, availability, extra services, etc.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-689773 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_channel_manager_bookings.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"wordpresss vacation rental system\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Channel Manager for Bookings<\\/h3>\\r\\nSynchronize all bookings submitted directly on your site with those from OTAs like Airbnb.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe system supports iCal sync enabling you to exchange booking data with the rental property directories where your accommodation is listed (make sure it supports iCal).\\r\\n\\r\\nAvoid overbooking without extra commissions and channel managers!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689772\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_online_offline_payments.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress property booking theme\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Online and Offline Payments<\\/h3>\\r\\nAccept online payments via many payment methods and increase your international travelers audience: PayPal, 2Checkout, Stripe, Braintree, Beanstream\\/Bambora, etc.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you need more gateways, you can easily add them with our custom WooCommerce Payments addon.\\r\\n\\r\\nGuest can pay a full \\/ deposit price or can be charged only after arrival. Optionally disable a booking functionality and simply display your rentals.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-689771 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_flexible_booking_rules.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"property managemenet system for wordpress\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Flexible Booking Rules<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe PMS allows you to set min \\/ max days to stay and available check-in and check-out dates for all rentals, accommodations individually or seasons.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also make certain accommodations unavailable for a chosen period of time (set not check-in, not check-out or not stay-in rules).\\r\\n\\r\\nOptionally customize accommodation rates by setting price variables based on a number of guests.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689770\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_booking_confirmation.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress booking system\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Booking Confirmation Modes<\\/h3>\\r\\nConfirm bookings automatically or manually, with or without a payment:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>by guest via email<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>by admin manually<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>by payment<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nNot confirmed bookings become \\u201cAbandoned\\u201d making the accommodation available for further reservation. The website admin can view the \\u201cAbandoned\\u201d bookings and get in touch with the prospective tenants via email.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-693045\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_weekly_montly_rates-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"alpenhouse weekly montly rates\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Weekly and Monthly Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou can set any room rate depending on a season (any term). To create different price points based on the length of stay, you can add weekly, monthly or other customizable rates.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe system will automatically discount the properties according to your rate rules. A better per-night rate for a longer stay will help you stay competitive in the industry!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689768\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_extra_services.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vacation rental services\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Extra Services<\\/h3>\\r\\nOffer bookable extra services or packages (free or paid) along with the accommodation reservation.\\r\\n\\r\\nCharge per room or per person. Guests can add any service to the cart when reserving your accommodation. You may also feature all available services on the website with all details.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-689767 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_taxes_fees.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"taxes and fees wordpress vacation rental theme alpenhouse\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>\\r\\nTaxes and Fees<\\/h3>\\r\\nComplete and correct pricing information on all accommodation charges: add mandatory fees, accommodation taxes, service taxes and fee taxes.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe guests will be able to see the summary of charges before making a booking. All this info on each booking is stored in the admin dashboard for easier accounting.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689766\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_discount_coupons.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"disounts property management system wordperss\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>\\r\\nDiscount Coupons<\\/h3>\\r\\nManually create discount coupons for loyal guests or to use in promo campaigns!\\r\\n\\r\\nYou\\u2019ll be able to set a discount amount, an expiration date, select accommodation types, set check-in and check-out dates, minimum and maximum days to stay and apply other settings to customize your coupons.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-689765 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_functional_headers.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"alpenhouse theme demo pages\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Functional Headers<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreate an eye-catching website header to give your website a unique look and feel: accompany your texts with a header image, slider, video or other content modules.\\r\\n\\r\\nCustomize any section easily with its own set of tools. Set up different header types for different website pages.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689763\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_elementor.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"elementor property rental wp theme\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Built with Elementor<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe theme is constructed with one of the most reliable WordPress Page Builder and different custom widgets.\\r\\n\\r\\nMove, edit and design the theme content with an absolutely user-friendly toolset. Use a library of ready-made Elementor templates on any page.\\r\\n\\r\\nThough AlpenHouse is made with Elementor, we didn\\u2019t lock the theme with it. You can edit it with MotoPress and other builders.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-689764 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_pre_built_modules.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"elementor wp theme for hotel\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Pre-built Modules for any Purpose<\\/h3>\\r\\nWe\\u2019ve packed this hotel booking WordPress theme with custom pre-designed content modules for all occasions: activities, trendy portfolio to present your lodging, extra services and packages, guest reviews, a contact form, accommodations and search availability related blocks and more.\\r\\n\\r\\nCustom settings are provided for each module to give you more customization flexibility. You can easily customize their layout on the frontend with Elementor.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689762\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_woocommerce.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"woocommerce hotel theme wp\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>WooCommerce Ready<\\/h3>\\r\\nBuild a stunning, well-categorized shop with the leading industry eCommerce plugin \\u2013 WooCommerce. Sell ski equipment, food baskets or any other products.\\r\\n\\r\\nStylish grid or list pre-designed shop templates are at your disposal.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-689760 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_blog_templates.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"rental property wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Blog Templates<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou\\u2019ll love the eye-catching and functional blog templates: a traditional blog layout with a sidebar, without sidebar and a Pinterest style layout with up to 3 columns.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour lodging news and articles will help you establish your brand and industry expertise extending your audience reach through social sharing.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-689761\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/alpenhouse_demo_data_import.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"demo data import\\\" width=\\\"432\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>1-Click Demo Data Import<\\/h3>\\r\\nImport sample data to the theme in one click and get your vacation rental website just like on the demo!\\r\\n\\r\\nThe data importer is packed with the theme, so you\\u2019ll be able to replace sample data with your custom content without any hassle.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>More about AlpenHouse Hotel Booking WordPress Theme:<\\/h3>\\r\\n<h4>Theme features:<\\/h4>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Simple setup and automated demo data import<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Mobile and Retina ready<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Live theme customizer<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>4 Home page and header design options<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Space for featuring an accommodation plan and facilities<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Custom Elementor widgets for your hotel, vacation rental, B&amp;B, cottage, etc.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>WooCommerce styling for online equipment store, ski shop, etc.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Image and video gallery portfolio (up to 4 columns layout)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Unique room layouts<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Guest reviews<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Masonry and standard blog layouts<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Fully customizable header and footer menus<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Social integration<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Custom post types for Activities<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Full-width and grid layouts<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>WPML support for multilingual websites<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Contact form 7 integrated<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Google Maps integrated<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Lightweight and extremely fast-loading<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>AlpenHouse child theme<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Widgets ready<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Priority support: a ticket system, live chat and email<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Fully documented.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h4>WordPress Booking system options:<\\/h4>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Premium <strong>MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">Hotel Booking plugin<\\/a><\\/strong> included for free (save $49)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Booking calendar for accommodations<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Re