ps:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/background_image_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Emmet background_image_image\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Hero Content Section<\\/h2>\\r\\nGrab visitor\\u2019s attention with the hero content - introduce yourself using a big title section. You are free to add the title and description to this section, customize the labels and links of the buttons or completely hide them. Your content will be displayed right onto the background image. Edit it in the WordPress Customizer in a real time.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667367\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/big_title_section_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"big_title_section_image emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Feature Section<\\/h2>\\r\\nStart adding more info about your brand within Feature sections: update the description, craft button labels and apply URLs to them, insert associated images. You may optionally set smooth animation effects for both content and the image. Emmet Lite comes with <em>2 sections of this type<\\/em>. If you need unlimited Feature sections, you need to get the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/emmet\\/\\\">Emmet Pro<\\/a> theme.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667369\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/first_feature_section_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"first_feature_section_image\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Colors<\\/h2>\\r\\nEmmet Lite allows you to change a default green color scheme to a blue, red or orange one. Moreover, you may set custom colors with a color picker: change a header text color, background color, text color, accent color, accent hover color, and a sub-menu hover color.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667370\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/colors.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"colors emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Call-to-action Section<\\/h2>\\r\\nUse this call-to-action section to guide your website visitors through the buying journey. You may customize the title and description of this section, change and link the buttons, control the appearance of content with the different fading animation effects. You may also set the position of this content block on the front page.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667371\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/call_2_action_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"call to action section emmet lite wp theme\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"361\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Multiple Features Section<\\/h2>\\r\\nThis is just the right section to briefly list your services or describe the benefits of your company. Here you\\u2019ll be able to edit the title, description and animation effects right in the Customizer. There are also lots of Font Awesome icons to use for your features. To add actual content of your features, you\\u2019ll need to go to Widgets &gt; Features section.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667372\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/features_section_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"features section emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Amazing Portfolio<\\/h2>\\r\\nAdd more imagery to your custom portfolio. Open this section in the WordPress Customizer to edit the title, description, animations effects and the section position on the front page. To add text and images to the actual portfolio projects, go to Dashboard &gt; Portfolio.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667373\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/portfolio_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"portfolio image emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Packages<\\/h2>\\r\\nIf you offer different pricing packages for your services, the comparison table may come in handy. To add all plans, you need to firstly add plans content with a Plan widget and then add it to Widgets &gt; Packages section. With the Customizer, you can edit the animation effects and the description of this section.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667375\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/packages_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"packages emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Team Section<\\/h2>\\r\\nShow the real people behind you company: tell about the team and show the members in the Team section. To add a photo, name and a position of every staff member, go to Customize &gt; Widgets &gt; Team section.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667376\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/team_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"team section emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Subscribe to Newsletter<\\/h2>\\r\\nEasily collect email addresses of the site visitors with a simple newsletter subscription form. All content and animation effects can be changed in the WordPress Customizer. Add the widget via Customize &gt; Widgets &gt; Subscribe section.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667377\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/newsletter_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"newsletter_image emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"361\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Testimonials<\\/h2>\\r\\nAdd testimonials in a stylish way - optionally make this block appear with custom animation. To add your testimonials to the front page, make sure to add the Testimonials widget via Customize &gt; Widgets &gt; Testimonials section.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667378\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/testimonials_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"testimonials emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Google Map Integration<\\/h2>\\r\\nEmmet Lite is integrated with Google maps - you just need to add a Google Map widget via Customize &gt; Widgets &gt; Google Map section. Your map with custom location markers will appear on the front page.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667379\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/google_map_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"google map emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Contact Form<\\/h2>\\r\\nEmmet Lite comes with a pre-built contact form, which can be customized by editing all essential fields like titles, descriptions, email address, etc. The form comes with reCaptcha protection ensuring your website is provided with the latest spam protection technology by Google. If you need a more complex form, you can replace this default form with your own form shortcode.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667380\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/contact_form_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"contact form emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Page Templates<\\/h2>\\r\\nWith Emmet Lite you can set different page templates: a full-width page, a header image page, a page with sidebar, and a landing page.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667381\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/page_templates_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"page templates image\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>WooCommerce Shop<\\/h2>\\r\\nEmmet Lite is fully compatible with WooCommerce plugin letting you create a professional online store.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667382\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/shop_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"woocommerce compatibility emmet lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>More Features of Emmet Lite<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Change the site identity: update the logo, favicon and a tagline<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Sticky menu on scroll<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Breadcrumbs<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Social integration - add links to any social media account<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Easily customizable menus<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Move or hide front page sections<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Parallax effects<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Apply your custom CSS<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>bbPress forum compatibility<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>MailChimp compatibility<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Emmet Lite vs Emmet Pro<\\/h2>\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><strong>Feature<\\/strong><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><strong>Emmet Lite<\\/strong><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><strong>Emmet Pro<\\/strong><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td>Video in header<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>-<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>+<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td>Unlimited Feature sections<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>-<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>+<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td>Content Editor Pro (save $29)<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>-<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>+<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<td>1 year of updates and support<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>-<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>+<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td>Edit or delete \\\"Designed by MotoPress\\\" text in footer<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>-<\\/td>\\r\\n<td>+<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a class=\\\"button button-lg\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/emmet\\/\\\">View Emmet Pro<\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"A one-page style free Multipurpose WordPress theme that is used by thousands of solopreneurs and agencies. Create your products and services portfolio, present a team, pricing add calls-to-action, change colors and more in a real time with WordPress Customizer.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/emmet_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 723,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 723,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"You found your best free WordPress themes collection - with no significant cut in functionality! Download for free a range of designs for creative and business projects.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642634,\n                \"slug\": \"oceanica-lite\",\n                \"title\": \"Oceanica Lite\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-08 20:11:53\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-04-23 13:57:44\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642634\",\n                \"content\": \"Oceanica Lite is extremely lightweight free WordPress theme for all sorts of blogs - travel blogs, hotel websites and more. It\\u2019s ready to give your website a fresh vibe thanks to a clean design, exceptional WordPress native portfolios, full-width and grid layouts, an outstanding blog and more.\\r\\n<h2>Header Image<\\/h2>\\r\\nAwesome header images are simply the featured images of your posts and pages. Make sure to upload high quality horizontal images.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667417\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/header_image-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"header image oceanica lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>Menus<\\/h2>\\r\\nOceanica Lite comes with 4 menu locations: a primary, header left, header right and footer. You may add different widgets to the footer menu via the WordPress Customizer.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667427\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/menu_image-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"oceanica lite menu\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>Testimonials<\\/h2>\\r\\nDisplay testimonials in a beautiful way with Jetpack plugin: add testimonials to the WordPress dashboard and then place a shortcode anywhere on the front page with a widget. This shortcode will create a slider featuring names and photos of people who left testimonials.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667428\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/testimonilas.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"testimonials oceanica\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>Featured Pages<\\/h2>\\r\\nCreate a stunning portfolio of your favorite services \\/ pages with a help of Jetpack plugin: use WordPress parent and child pages to create native WordPress galleries.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/featured_pages_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"child and parent pages\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-671289\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>Post Meta Data<\\/h2>\\r\\nTo display more details about your posts, you may output post metadata right in the list of posts: a post author, a publishing date, categories, tags, and a link to leave comments.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667429\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/post_meta_image-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"post meta data oceanica lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>Customizable Colors<\\/h2>\\r\\nThere are several options to change your colors: a background color, the main text color, link color, and a button hover color.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667430\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/colors-2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"customizable colors oceanica lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>Page Templates<\\/h2>\\r\\nOceanica Lite offers several page layouts: full-width, full-width grid, and full-width with sidebar.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667431\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/features.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"page templates oceanica lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>WooCommerce Ready<\\/h2>\\r\\nOceanica Lite comes with a pre-made design for WooCommerce shop, so you can start selling your products or services faster and easier.\\r\\n<img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667435\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/woocommerce.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"woocommerce plugin oceanica lite\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you are looking for a WordPress hotel business theme with a fully functional room reservation system (rates, seasons, services, real-time search availability form, online payments, etc.), check out <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/oceanica\\/\\\">Oceanica Hotel Booking theme<\\/a> on our website. It\'s fully integrated with our MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">Hotel Booking plugin<\\/a> letting you feature rooms listing in a beautiful way and enable instant paid bookings.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Oceanica Lite is a free hotel WordPress theme with a minimal design for your hotel business, travel blog or travel agency. The theme is fully responsive providing a great user experience for all devices. You\\u2019ll love a neat typography and focus on imagery for uncluttered and attention-to-details blogging.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/oceanica_lite_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 723,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 723,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"You found your best free WordPress themes collection - with no significant cut in functionality! Download for free a range of designs for creative and business projects.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642632,\n                \"slug\": \"avior\",\n                \"title\": \"Avior\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-08 20:11:33\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-04-11 13:53:08\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642632\",\n                \"content\": \"Avior is a lightweight and stylish free WordPress theme for bloggers. It comes with a neat design and on-balance layouts making it perfectly suitable for a personal, food, travel, or any other sort of a blog. This distinctive search engines optimized theme will help you stand out of the crowd and create impressive posts that will look just perfect on any modern device.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Customizable Header and Footer<\\/h2>\\r\\nChange footer and header info with ease: link your social media accounts to the already integrated social media icons, create an informative footer, change a header image (header size is 1920 \\u00d7 200 pixels), and more.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/header_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"header_image avior\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667399\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Flexible Menus<\\/h2>\\r\\nAvior comes with 3 flexible menus: primarily, social and footer. You may add different text content, links, images and widgets to them.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/menu_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"menu image avior\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667400\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Post Meta Data<\\/h2>\\r\\nOptionally display information about your posts: a post author, a publishing date, categories, tags, and a link to leave comments.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/post_meta_image.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"avior free blogging theme\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667401\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Customizable Colors<\\/h2>\\r\\nSet any color easily in a real time via WordPress Customizer: change a header text color, a background color, a header background color, a footer background color, a text color, a link color, and a button hover color.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/colors-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"colors avior\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667402\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Page Templates<\\/h2>\\r\\nWith Avior you can blog using a destruction-free full-width page template or a traditional layout with a sidebar.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/templates.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"page templates avior\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667403\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>WooCommerce Compatibility<\\/h2>\\r\\nIf you plan to sell anything with WooCommerce, Avior comes with a ready-made shop design.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/04\\/shop_image-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"shop image avior\\\" width=\\\"891\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667404\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Avior is a clean and dandy free WordPress theme, designed for people, who aim for photo-rich and SEO-smart writing. It lets you change footer and header info like menus and social media icons, change header image, use unlimited colors to reach a perfect color scheme and more.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/avior_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 723,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 723,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"You found your best free WordPress themes collection - with no significant cut in functionality! Download for free a range of designs for creative and business projects.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642629,\n                \"slug\": \"timetable-event-schedule\",\n                \"title\": \"Timetable & Event Schedule\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-08 20:09:01\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-02-22 17:32:31\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642629\",\n                \"content\": \"<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-responsive-design.png\\\" alt=\\\"responsive design\\\" \\/>Responsive Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nWordPress Timetable plugin provides your audience with a proper tablet and mobile viewing of the timetable and upcoming events widgets.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt offers you more freedom of responsive design customization implemented by two alternatives: you can set it to either standard table view or responsive modern list view for mobiles. This setting can be applied in the timetable shortcode.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-shortcodes-toolkit.png\\\" alt=\\\"custom categories\\\" \\/>Toolkit of Shortcode Settings<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe toolkit doesn\\u2019t require any cross-functional or coding skills. \\r\\n\\r\\nWordPress Timetable plugin added via TinyMCE is supplied with parameters to help you maximum adjust the timetable to your needs and website design. Each setting is accompanied with sufficient clarifications to ensure you coordinate and edit your events fast without additional help. \\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/full-control-of-event-parameters.png\\\" alt=\\\"various menu designs\\\" \\/>Full Control of Event Parameters<\\/h3>\\r\\nScheduling plugin for WordPress works perfectly for various classes, trainings, workshops, conferences, formal parties, concerts, non-profits, and nearly any other type of event as a set of event details for the timetable is rather universal. Using the plugin, you can edit the needed parameters your visitors expect to see while searching for the needed event: title, subtitle, time, event head, images, detailed event description, and time slots (if there are many for one event).\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-event-filtering.png\\\" alt=\\\"import|export menu items\\\" \\/>Easy Event Filtering <\\/h3>\\r\\nThe search results can be easily refined using the filters by events. The functionality of the plugin allows you to apply two filter styles: tabs to show all events at a time or drop-down list. The site visitors can easily filter the timetable to display the only events they are interested in. It\\u2019s very reliable in terms of navigation and guarantees the website visitors good times.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-upcoming-events.png\\\" alt=\\\"unlimited delicious images\\\" \\/>Upcoming Events<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe Upcoming events widget helps to keep the sidebar of your site clutter-free and to present all the future events in a stylish and elegant list style. It\\u2019ll duplicate design settings of the actual timetable, but will look more compact. The widget is entirely hidden when no upcoming events are scheduled. This feature increases the usability of the timetable and helps to guide the site visitors faster.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-parameters-contorl.png\\\" alt=\\\"helpful widgets\\\" \\/>Powerful Schedule Functionality<\\/h3>\\r\\nEase of navigation, fast-loading events and clean design are key factors able to increase a happy user experience; a lot of shortcode options ensure that your timetable runs so and is customized the way you want. For example, you can manually adjust the row height to size the timetable according to the number of events and information output into one event cell, link particular events to external websites, and even automatically export\\/import timetable data during backup or changing hosting.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-flexible-timeframes.png\\\" alt=\\\"sell food and beverages online\\\" \\/>Flexible Timeframes<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe left \\u2018time\\u2019 column can show up to 15 minutes accurate time apart from standard hourly and half-hourly time frames. It lets you make the timetable more visually balanced and attractive depending on the amount of events and row height set within shortcode. If any unexpected delays or changes take place, your timetable can bend easily in one direction or another thanks to a couple of quick time edits in the shortcode settings.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-professional-support.png\\\" alt=\\\"Integrated with MotoPress Builder\\\" \\/>Professional Support<\\/h3>\\r\\nIf you believe the timetable lacks any necessary feature, give us this good food for thought. Our professionals want to improve the plugin in terms of essential functionality and of course solve all possible problems along the way. The process starts simple, contact our support representatives and they won\\u2019t you keep waiting. The plugin is fully compatible with MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/content-editor\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Page Builder<\\/a> and also with <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/wordpress-slider\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Slider<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<p>Download <a href=\\\"\\/files\\/timetable_demo_29.08.2016.xml\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Demo Content (xml)<\\/a><\\/p>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Free WordPress Event Schedule plugin will help you create a clean-looking calendar of events with custom column names, details, event head avatars and background colors. A user-friendly toolkit is provided - add your events, configure settings and your timetable is ready.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timetable_event_schedule_plugin.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 722,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 722,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Download multipurpose and niche free WordPress plugins. Optional extra functionality for almost all plugins is available!\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 700,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 700,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Free and premium WordPress plugins for your website. We ensure you get products created according to WordPress coding standards, niche-focused functionality and overall customization flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642627,\n                \"slug\": \"another-mailchimp-widget\",\n                \"title\": \"Another MailChimp Widget\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-08 20:07:33\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-02-22 09:10:29\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642627\",\n                \"content\": \"This plugin lets your users sign up for your MailChimp lists and groups via subscription form added through widget or shortcode.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Shortcode example:<\\/h3>\\r\\n<pre>&#91;mp-mc-form list=\\u201dlist_id\\/group_id\\u201d button=\\u201dSubscribe\\u201d