         \"term_taxonomy_id\": 722,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Download multipurpose and niche free WordPress plugins. Optional extra functionality for almost all plugins is available!\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 700,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 700,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Free and premium WordPress plugins for your website. We ensure you get products created according to WordPress coding standards, niche-focused functionality and overall customization flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642619,\n                \"slug\": \"restaurant-menu\",\n                \"title\": \"Restaurant Menu\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-08 20:05:39\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-03-01 10:36:09\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642619\",\n                \"content\": \"<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/03\\/rm_addons.png\\\" alt=\\\"Restaurant Menu Addons\\\" width=\\\"532\\\" height=\\\"341\\\" class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-651498\\\" \\/>Restaurant Menu Add-ons<\\/h3>\\r\\nThanks to the Restaurant Menu add-ons you are able to offer extremely beneficial and suitable options and make customer experience really valuable. Moreover, it\\u2019s easy to raise clients\\u2019 loyalty and improve retention due to the simplicity and convenience of these additional tools.\\r\\n\\r\\n<a class=\\\"button more-link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/category\\/restaurant-menu-addons\\/\\\">Restaurant Menu Addons<\\/a>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/purchase-online-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"sell food and beverages online\\\" \\/>Sell Food and Beverages Online<\\/h3>\\r\\nTake your sales to the next level allowing the visitors to make a purchase online via a secure and popular payment system.\\r\\n\\r\\nPlacing an order, your customers will be able to choose a payment method: PayPal or Cash on delivery. Both registered and unregistered users can make a purchase. The system also provides your buyers with the order statuses (processing, shipping and shipped) and confirmation\\/notification emails.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/responsive-design-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"responsive design\\\" \\/>Responsive Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nIt\'s highly important for your online menu to look awesome on each device of everyone on the go. The Restaurant menu plugin guarantees optimal viewing on all mobile devices including small ones. The images of the menu items and categories look sharp and the texts are fully readable without scrolling.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/unlimited-custom-categories-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"custom categories\\\" \\/>Unlimited Custom Categories<\\/h3>\\r\\nConstruct categorically-organized lists of food and drinks (e.g. breakfast, lunch, dinner; drinks menu, desserts menu; breakfast on the go, casual meals, holiday menu, etc.) for easy search and navigation through the menu. Admin tools allow customizing each category by adding an appropriate image, title, description and icon (standard or custom). You are also free to create a child category for each parent one if there are a lot of menu items.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/various-menu-designs-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"various menu designs\\\" \\/>Various Menu Designs<\\/h3>\\r\\nIt\'s absolutely up to your taste how the online menu should be presented. We made sure the plugin works perfectly for any design. Grid or list layout can be applied to menu items and categories allowing you to find the best way to display your menu depending on the number of items or categories, website design and width. Several settings in shortcode parameters will do all this magic for you.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/import-export-menu-items-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"import|export menu items\\\" \\/>Import & Export Menu Items<\\/h3>\\r\\nAll the necessary tweaks of moving your site to a new host or simple backup won\'t affect the data created with a help of the WordPress Restaurant menu plugin in any way. You can safely export and import all the menu items and categories to further use on other websites and continue making your updates. It\'s quite a simple process and involves a couple of clicks within your WordPress admin panel.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/unlimited-images-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"unlimited delicious images\\\" \\/>Unlimited Delicious Images<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe photos of your dishes are a true reality each customer is looking for. Spice up the online presence of your restaurant or cafe with attractive images to conquer each visitor at a first glance. The functionality of the plugin allows you setting a featured image for any menu item, menu category, and to supply each menu item with an individual image gallery. A picture is always worth a thousand words, show how tasty your items are with unlimited number of images and await for a lot of fans!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/helpful-widgets-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"helpful widgets\\\" \\/>Helpful Widgets<\\/h3>\\r\\nAdd a carefully organized menu as a sidebar widget and let it always be at hand of any website visitor. You can choose whether to display the entire menu or just some particular hot offerings. It will look perfect on desktops and will be automatically adjusted for proper mobile viewing. A great way to keep your sidebar useful and clutter-free at the same time.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/integrated-drag-and-drop-builder-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"Integrated with MotoPress Builder\\\" \\/>Integrated with MotoPress Builder<\\/h3>\\r\\nCan you name any better alternative for editing the website than WYSIWYG solution? Thanks to the full integration of the WordPress Restaurant Menu plugin with the MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/content-editor\\/\\\">WordPress Page Builder<\\/a> you are free to play around with each setting online and choose the best way to show your menu much faster and easier than through default shortcode added in the TinyMCE. Setting up the menu via the Content Editor you\'ll see all the menu elements directly in the site area and will edit the appearance of the menu visually. Works perfectly with MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/wordpress-slider\\/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Slider<\\/a>.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/restaurant-menu\\/profssional-support-restaurant-menu-wordpress-plugin.png\\\" alt=\\\"professional support\\\" \\/>Professional Support<\\/h3>\\r\\nIf you noticed any bug or have a scarcely useful proposition on how to improve the plugin, let your voice be heard! MotoPress support representatives are always ready to answer your questions and discuss ideas in a timely manner. Professional tech guys are always keep looking for better options and are eager to put into use everything they learn from the users.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Demo Content<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"\\/files\\/restaurantmenu_demo_11.01.2017.xml\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Download Demo Content (xml)<\\/a><\\/p>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"A user-friendly WordPress plugin to build your restaurant or cafe website and sell food and beverages online. Stunning tasty designs, ultimate item description with nutrition info, Food Delivery and Toppings extensions for extra functionality.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/restaurant_menu_plugin.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 722,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 722,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Download multipurpose and niche free WordPress plugins. Optional extra functionality for almost all plugins is available!\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 700,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 700,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Free and premium WordPress plugins for your website. We ensure you get products created according to WordPress coding standards, niche-focused functionality and overall customization flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 631792,\n                \"slug\": \"hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\",\n                \"title\": \"Hotel Booking WooCommerce Payments\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-01-18 10:49:35\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-07-18 08:28:39\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=631792\",\n                \"content\": \"This plugin integrates WooCommerce payment gateways with MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">Hotel Booking plugin for WordPress<\\/a>. Use it to extend a number of payment gateways needed to handle online reservation of accommodations.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Backend demo<\\/h2>\\r\\nTo test backend of Hotel Booking WooCommerce Payments add-on, register your demo: click View Demo button and choose Villagio theme.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>How to install the addon<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n \\t<li>Install and activate the plugin.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Create one WooCommerce product (e.g. Reservation) that will be used for reservations.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Navigate to Hotel Booking settings page, activate \\u201cWooCommerce\\u201d payment and select created product.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Set up WooCommerce payment gateways.<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments-settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"856\\\" height=\\\"541\\\" class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-643397\\\" \\/><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>How it will work for your guests<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n \\t<li>Your guest chooses the accommodation on your site.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Guest provides personal data to confirm the reservation.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Guest chooses from the WooCommerce payment gateways offered by you and pays.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments-checkout.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1080\\\" height=\\\"1610\\\" class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-643398\\\" \\/><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>A new booking appears upon successful payment.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments-bookings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"856\\\" height=\\\"386\\\" class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-643395\\\" \\/><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>WooCommerce orders are automatically synchronized with bookings of Hotel Booking plugin.\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments-woocommerce-orders.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"856\\\" height=\\\"378\\\" class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-643396\\\" \\/><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Requirements:<\\/h4>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\">Hotel Booking plugin<\\/a> 2.4.0 or greater;<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/woocommerce\\/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">WooCommerce plugin<\\/a> 3.2.6 or greater;<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This plugin integrates WooCommerce payment gateways with MotoPress Hotel Booking plugin for WordPress. Use it to extend a number of payment gateways needed to handle online reservation of accommodations.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/01\\/woocommerce_plugin.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 700,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 700,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Free and premium WordPress plugins for your website. We ensure you get products created according to WordPress coding standards, niche-focused functionality and overall customization flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"89.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"178.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 569902,\n                \"slug\": \"creatista\",\n                \"title\": \"Creatista\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2017-09-13 11:34:53\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-05-21 14:14:59\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=569902\",\n                \"content\": \"<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-569951\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/09\\/creatista_perfect_for_creatives.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress portfilio theme creatista\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Perfect for Creatives<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe theme features a minimal hand-crafted design for a variety of creative fields: illustrations, cartooning, product design, fan art, polygraphy, hand-sketching and other creative fields.\\r\\n\\r\\nArchitect and interior designers can also find a home for their projects with Creatista. The projects based on motion graphic, 3D characters, cinema design, caricatures will also look great thanks to wide-screen layouts where all the charts and photos of all sorts and sizes will look great.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-569952\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/09\\/creatista_mobile_ready_minimalist_design.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress portfolio theme creatista\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Mobile-ready Minimalist Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreatista is 100% responsive. We\\u2019ve done the biggest thing we could: minimized theme elements and maximized the space for showcasing your works.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe theme will deliver all types of website content in the most suitable dimension across all desktops, mobiles and tablets. It will be easy to impress and engage the owner of any device!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-569954\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/09\\/creatista_beautiful_projects.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress portfolio theme creatista\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Beautiful Projects<\\/h3>\\r\\nWant to feature a graphic novel? Book cover design? Detailed product design charts? Poster illustrations?\\r\\n\\r\\nDo whatever you want inside individual projects of your WordPress portfolio - add images, texts, video, audio and play around with the position of content elements easily. Fixed width and full pages are available.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-569955\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/09\\/creatista_jetpack_portfolio.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress creative portfolio theme creatista\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Jetpack Portfolio<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe portfolio is powered by the Jetpack plugin - a top professional WordPress plugin used by millions. It gives you lots of options to modify the look and feel of your portfolio, featuring individual works and projects by different categories.\\r\\n\\r\\nAdditionally, you may use tons of other useful free Jetpack features to power your website.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-569956\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/09\\/creatista_quick_setup_customization.png\\\" alt=\\\"creatista creative portfolio theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Quick Setup and Customization<\\/h3>\\r\\nWe take care of your website performance and SEO! That is why you\\u2019ll enjoy the theme that is not overwhelmed with confusing settings you may lose control over.\\r\\n\\r\\nAdd and customize your projects, set up the front page, add social links - and your creative portfolio is ready! If you need more help, docs and support chat is always at hand!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-569957\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/09\\/creatista_social_ready_single_projects.png\\\" alt=\\\"creative wordpress portfolio theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Social Integration<\\/h3>\\r\\nIt\\u2019s easy to engage people and make your works popular!\\r\\n\\r\\nThe site visitors can view and share your projects via different social networks, preview the images in original size, and comment under each photo or project.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-680377\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/05\\/creatista_woocommerce_ready.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress woocommerce theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>WooCommerce Shop<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreatista comes with a shop design that looks just perfect for an integrated WooCommerce plugin.\\r\\n\\r\\nSet up a shop easily with the industry leading e-commerce plugin, sell arts while staying at home!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"A perfect WordPress Portfolio theme for creative works of designers, illustrators and other artists. You\\u2019ll enjoy balanced minimal layouts, flexible portfolios and a seamless installation process.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/creatista_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"55.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 560790,\n                \"slug\": \"villagio\",\n                \"title\": \"Villagio\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2017-08-21 08:20:41\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-09-19 09:34:14\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=560790\",\n                \"content\": \"<h2 style=\\\"text-align:center;\\\">Property Rental WordPress Theme Highlights<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-560035\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_accommodation_reservation_engine.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress property rental theme\\\" width=\\\"461\\\" height=\\\"423\\\" \\/>Accommodation Reservation System<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreate a listing of your accommodations and enable live reservations with our custom MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Hotel Booking plugin<\\/a> for WordPress. You\\u2019ll simply need to add your content, configure general settings, turn on online reservations and add the generated shortcodes into the site pages. You may feature the amenities of the property, photos, description, size, bed types, capacity, extra services, etc.\\r\\nDisable booking option any time.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560036\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_multiple_accommodations.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_multiple_accommodations.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_multiple_accommodations-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"multiple property booking wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Rent out Multiple Accommodations<\\/h3>\\r\\nWant to rent out different accommodations in a variety of locations? Simply add each villa, guest house, apartment, etc. as a different accommodation type. To find the needed accommodation, users will need to sort them by categories you set (e.g. region, type, cost).\\r\\n\\r\\nNote: the category is not included into the search availability form, so the guest will need first find the needed accommodation by the region and then check its availability.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-560038\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_real_time_search.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_real_time_search.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_real_time_search-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"search availability form\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Real-time Search Availability Form<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe search availability form is very easy to use for guests and always shows the correct number of available.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe booking process in this WordPress Property Rental theme is automated (accommodations are blocked immediately upon payments if you set it so), so you don\\u2019t need to make any efforts to control reservations.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560039\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_seasonal_pricing_rates.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_seasonal_pricing_rates.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_seasonal_pricing_rates-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"customizable seasons and rates\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Seasonal Pricing<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe pricing system is very flexible \\u2013 you may set different accommodation prices depending on seasons or dates.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you want to rent out the accommodation with different benefits and conditions, simply create different rates with different pricing accordingly (e.g. refundable and non-refundable.)\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/villagio_variable_rates.png\\\" alt=\\\"rates vacation rental theme\\\" width=\\\"458\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-693043\\\" \\/>Weekly and Monthly Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou can set any room rate depending on a season (any term). To create different price points based on the length of stay, you can add weekly, monthly or other customizable rates. For example, you can set any number of days and apply a needed per-night price based on the length of stay.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe system will automatically discount the properties according to your rate rules. A better per-night rate for a longer stay will help you stay competitive in the industry!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-560040 alignright\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_online_offline_payments.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_online_offline_payments.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_online_offline_payments-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"payments wordpress property rental theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Online and Offline Payments<\\/h3>\\r\\nVillagio vacation rental WordPress theme allows you accept online reservation payments through many payment methods, increasing your international travelers audience: PayPal, 2Checkout, Stripe, Braintree, Beanstream\\/Bambora, and more. If you need more gateways, you can additionally purchase our custom <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\"> WooCommerce Payments addon<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\nGuest can pay a full or deposit price. Moreover, you may allow your guests pay only after arrival. Pending payment time is editable.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/villagio_pricing_variables.png\\\" alt=\\\"vacation rental theme variable pricing\\\" width=\\\"458\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-693044\\\" \\/>Variable Pricing<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe accommodation rate can be changed automatically depending on a number of guests. You simply need to add a needed number of the per-guest price variables that will be different from the base accommodation price.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour guests will see a relative price once they input their search parameters.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560041\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_services_packages.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_services_packages.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_services_packages-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress property rental theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Packages and Services<\\/h3>\\r\\nSell or offer for free extra services and packages \\u2013 the guests can pre-order them when placing a booking request.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe price can be set either per room or per person. A really great way to engage clients and earn more!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-560042\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_date_blocking.png?19122017\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_date_blocking.png 458w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_date_blocking-300x210.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"date blocking wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Flexible Booking Rules<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe PMS allows you to set min \\/ max days to stay and available check-in and check-out dates for all rentals, accommodations individually or seasons.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also block booking option for all accommodations or any one individually for a chosen period of time (set not check-in, not check-out or not stay-in rules).\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560043\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_booking_confirmation.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_booking_confirmation.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_booking_confirmation-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"booking confirmation property rental wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Manual and Automatic Booking Confirmation<\\/h3>\\r\\nSet the WordPress booking system to confirm reservations instantly upon the payment or do it manually via the email.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also configure the reservation plugin to confirm the bookings automatically without a payment.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-585240\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2016\\/12\\/booking-ical_support.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2016\\/12\\/booking-ical_support.png 467w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2016\\/12\\/booking-ical_support-300x202.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"motopress hotel booking plugin for wordpress\\\" width=\\\"467\\\" height=\\\"314\\\" \\/>Channel Manager for Bookings<\\/h3>\\r\\nSynchronize all reservations submitted directly on your site with those on OTAs like <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/booking.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Booking.com<\\/a> or Airbnb. The system supports iCal sync, which means you can exchange booking data with the channels where your property is listed and avoid overbooking.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe synchronization is possible only with those OTAs that support iCal file format (the most popular ones do.)\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560044\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_automatic_reservation.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_automatic_reservation.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_automatic_reservation-300x215.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress propery rental theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"330\\\" \\/>All Sorts of Emails<\\/h3>\\r\\nTransform booking email notifications into your brand emails with a help of email settings and handy macros.\\r\\n\\r\\nAutomate the process of sending admin and user notifications. The system supports a new booking, confirmation, and cancellation types of emails.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-560045\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_discount_coupons.png\\\" alt=\\\"discounts property rental wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"430\\\" \\/>Discount Coupons<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreate coupons with different parameters and please your guests with discounts!\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may add unlimited number of coupons, customize them and give guests to apply on the checkout page. You are free to set the amount of discount in percent, choose expiration date, set limit, etc.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560046\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_admin_calendar.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_admin_calendar.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_admin_calendar-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress property rental theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Admin Calendar of Bookings<\\/h3>\\r\\nPreview all bookings by dates in a handy calendar format.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also view the payment history of each booking in details \\u2013 see all statuses, amounts of payments and all guest details. You may also check all bookings on a list view.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-560047\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_responsive_balanced_design.png\\\" alt=\\\"responsive design of a property rental theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"446\\\" \\/>Responsive and Balanced Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nGet a perfect alignment, balance and contrast of content modules with the clean design of Villagio Property Rental WordPress theme. The theme is 100% responsive making it easy to book an accommodation from any device.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe theme demo is translated with a help of <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wpml.org\\/?aid=215265&amp;affiliate_key=ulbcgJ1lxxoI\\\"> WPML plugin<\\/a> - one of the best multilingual WordPress plugins, so you can easily add a language switcher to your site (WPML plugin is not included into the theme).\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560048\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_boxed_wide_layouts.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_boxed_wide_layouts.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_boxed_wide_layouts-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"property rental wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Boxed and Wide Layouts<\\/h3>\\r\\nBoxed and wide layouts are at your disposal.\\r\\n\\r\\nUse different layouts depending on a page type: you may choose from full-width, grid or full-width grid templates to list accommodation types, extra services, etc.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-560052\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_header_slider.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_header_slider.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_header_slider-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"property renral wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Header Slider<\\/h3>\\r\\nPromote the chosen accommodations by showcasing them on the front page in a stylish and informative header slider \\u2013 simply select the names of accommodations and choose what details to display.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may add it through the Accommodation types widget via the WordPress Customizer to the theme widget area. You may replace the slider widget with any other if you want.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-560053\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_guest_reviews.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_guest_reviews.png 460w, https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/villagio_guest_reviews-300x209.png 300w\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress property rental theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Guest Reviews<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou may add and customize the look of the guest reviews with the Testimonials widget powered by the professional Jetpack plugin.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe plugin allows to upload the photos of guests and add their reviews.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Villagio is a fully functional Property Rental WordPress theme that can be used for renting out multiple accommodations: villas, guest houses, apartments, etc. Feature your accommodations in a beautiful way and enable instant bookings via WordPress reservation system.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/villagio_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 844,\n                        \"name\": \"Hotel and Property Rental WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"hotel-rental-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 844,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Vacation rental WordPress themes and Hotel themes with the built-in WordPress Hotel Booking plugin by MotoPress included for free.\\r\\n\\r\\nThese property rental WordPress themes will definitely help you display the facilities and advantages of your single property website, small family hotel, elite boutique, hostel or cosy apartment for rent. Each template is beautifully designed, well-structured and equipped with easy booking tool - WordPress Booking plugin. \\r\\n\\r\\nMotoPress WordPress reservation plugin offers easy property management system, an iCal channel manager for OTAs, built-in payment gateways, offline and online payments, availability calendar, extra services, booking calendar, custom rates, seasonal pricing, taxes & fees, discount coupons and much more.\\r\\n\\r\\nUse this perfect combo of Hotel Booking Plugin and WordPress real estate theme and build your successful business with MotoPress\\r\\n\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 7,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"59.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.5.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 554351,\n                \"slug\": \"niftyfifty\",\n                \"title\": \"Niftyfifty\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2017-08-07 15:19:44\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-04-13 08:43:22\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=554351\",\n                \"content\": \"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=AA6vYASCj1Q\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-554670\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_clean_minimal_design.png\\\" alt=\\\"photogrpahy wordpress theme minimal design\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Clean and Minimal Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nStylish and minimal design approach is the future of web design thanks to its usability and richness. You\\u2019ll please the site visitors with a smart navigation and clutter-free space.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Nifty Fifty WordPress theme is 100% responsive and retina-ready.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-554671\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_dark_and_light_skins.png\\\" alt=\\\"dark and light skins photography wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Dark and Light Skins<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe look and feel of your photography website depends a lot on the main color scheme. You may choose and set the preferable skin with just one click via the visual WordPress Customizer.\\r\\n\\r\\nPowerful <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/themes.getmotopress.com\\/niftyfifty\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">dark<\\/a> or elegant <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/themes.getmotopress.com\\/niftyfifty-white\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">light<\\/a> theme skins are at your disposal.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-554672\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_stylish_masonry_layout.png\\\" alt=\\\"masonry layouts photographer portfolio wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Stylish Masonry Layout<\\/h3>\\r\\nDynamic and clean Pinterest style layouts will easily support the photos of variable sizes, without unintelligent cropping. Portfolios galleries are created with a help of the Jetpack plugin letting you organize your works with a top professional WordPress plugin. You may set the preferable columns number, info to display, and divide the photos into categories.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-554673\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_social_ready_single_projects.png\\\" alt=\\\"social ready photographer portfolio wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Social-ready Projects<\\/h3>\\r\\nThanks to a great social media integration, people can view and share any of the projects on social networks, view full image sizes, comment under each photo or under the entire project of your photographer portfolio. The photos in a single project are listed with mobile navigation in mind, so it\\u2019s really easy to engage the visitors on mobile and tablet devices as well.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-554674\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_handy_navigation.png\\\" alt=\\\"handy navigation photography wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Handy Navigation<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe overall theme navigation is a well thought-out process: a tiny hamburger menu to make the main focus on your photos and handy buttons to switch across different projects are very helpful.\\r\\n\\r\\nA simple photos listing makes it easy even for the mobile users to view the photos in the best quality.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-554675\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_intelligent_image_rendering.png\\\" alt=\\\"intelligent image rendering photogrpahy wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Intelligent Image Rendering<\\/h3>\\r\\nKeep all your photos authentically perfect across all devices. The Nifty Fifty theme uses a better way to deal with responsive images - \\u2018srcset\\u2019 attribute. It will automatically define a device-pixel ratio to show each photo in the most suitable way depending on the device used. You may rest assured that your images are well optimized for the search engines.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-554676\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_seo_literate.png\\\" alt=\\\"SEO ready photography wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>SEO-literate<\\/h3>\\r\\nThis WordPress theme is extremely fast-loading and lightweight, which is essentially important for showcasing your photography craft.\\r\\n\\r\\nNo wrong and redundant tools, individual URL for each image, alt tags, meta info, etc. are all crucial components of the Nifty Fifty Photographer portfolio WordPress theme.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-554677\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/08\\/niftyfifty_native_wordPress_theme.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress native theme photography theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Native WordPress Theme<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou may not be afraid to be locked down with any theme engine as this photography theme is maximum WordPress native.\\r\\n\\r\\nSo, in case you want to switch the theme (we guarantee you won\\u2019t!), all your content will stay on the site. A perfect deal for any photography project.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Minimalist WordPress Photography theme crafted for creatives: photographers, illustrators, designers and artists. Flexible portfolios, black and white theme skins, distinctive design \\u2013 all you need to present yourself authentically.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/nify_fifty_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"55.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 528013,\n                \"slug\": \"oceanica\",\n                \"title\": \"Oceanica\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2017-06-01 07:45:17\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-09-19 08:06:49\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=528013\",\n                \"content\": \"<h2 style=\\\"text-align:center;\\\">WordPress Hotel Theme Highlights<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536087\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-elegant-intuitive-design.png\\\" alt=\\\"elegant intuitive design\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Elegant Intuitive Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nWe\\u2019ve used the best design techniques to make Oceanica WordPress hotel theme visually perfect and reach a design-usability balance.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe ease of navigation, intuitiveness and a clutter-free page space are what your guests will enjoy when surfing the site.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-538521\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-responsive-and-mobile-ready-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"responsive and mobile ready\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Responsive and Mobile Ready<\\/h3>\\r\\nSharp and clean content on each device, no matter the screen size.\\r\\n\\r\\nBe sure that modern travelers will be able to make an online room reservation from the cell phone as easy as desktop users.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536090\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-customizable-front-page.png\\\" alt=\\\"customizable front page wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Fully Customizable Front Page<\\/h3>\\r\\nThis WordPress hotel theme is fully integrated with the WordPress Customizer for editing the front page in a real time - simply add and style your content without any coding.\\r\\n\\r\\nWith a little configuration even not-tech WordPress users will bring the site online pretty fast.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-536091\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-unlimited-colors.png\\\" alt=\\\"unlimited colors wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Unlimited Colors<\\/h3>\\r\\nCreate the color scheme that will perfectly suit your needs - your feel, your colors, your brand.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt\\u2019s easy to change the colors in clicks with the color picker via the WordPress customizer live editor.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536093\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-customization-menu.png\\\" alt=\\\"customizable menu wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Customizable Menus<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou won\\u2019t need to get any extra toolkit to manage menus. Current 3 header and 1 footer menus are absolutely editable - you can use any to feature your primary pages, contact info, social media icons, or anything else you want. Switch menu location and update their content any time.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-536098\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-wide-and-boxed-layouts.png\\\" alt=\\\"wide and boxed layouts wordpress theme\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Wide and Boxed Layouts<\\/h3>\\r\\nUse different layouts for different needs.\\r\\n\\r\\nThere are several page templates you can use on your site - full width, with sidebar, full width grid, grid with sidebar. Each one is a hand-crafted design solution.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536099\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-integration-with-wordpress.png\\\" alt=\\\"theme with native integration with wordpress\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Native Integration with WordPress<\\/h3>\\r\\nOceanica WordPress hotel theme is maximum integrated with a native WordPress core functionality, so the editing process will be a breeze for you.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou won\\u2019t lose your content even if you switch the theme.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-536101\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-hotel-booking-engine.png\\\" alt=\\\"wordpress theme with hotel room booking engine\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Hotel Booking Engine [free]<\\/h3>\\r\\nProfessionally translated into multiple languages, our premium <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">WordPress Reservation Plugin<\\/a> is included for free into this theme.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe plugin will help you create an awesome rooms listing and optionally enable online reservation for them to fully automate your work with the guests.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536102\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-payment-systems.png\\\" alt=\\\"online and offline hotel reservation payments\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Online and Offline Payments<\\/h3>\\r\\nPayPal, 2Checkout, Stripe, Braintree, Beanstream\\/Bambora, and more to come. For more gateways, you can purchase our custom <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/hotel-booking-woocommerce-payments\\/\\\">WooCommerce Payments add-on<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou can accept online reservation payments through these payment methods, increasing your international travellers audience. Moreover, you may allow your guests pay only after arrival.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-536103\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-seasonal-pricing.png\\\" alt=\\\"seasonal prices for hotel booking\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Seasonal Pricing and Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nSet different prices for low and high seasons, weekends, or whatever period you want - the plugin settings allow you to apply these changes in a matter of clicks.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-619926\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-flexible-booking-rules.png\\\" alt=\\\"oceanica custom booking rules\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Custom Booking Rules<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe PMS allows you to set min \\/ max days to stay and available check-in and check-out dates for all rooms at once, accommodations individually or seasons.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also block booking option for all accommodations or any one individually for a chosen period of time (set not check-in, not check-out or not stay-in rules).\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-693038\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/oceanica-weekly-monthly-rates.png\\\" alt=\\\"oceanica-weekly-monthly-rates\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Weekly and Monthly Rates<\\/h3>\\r\\nYou can set any room rate depending on a season (any term). To create different price points based on the length of stay, you can add weekly, monthly or other customizable rates.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe system will automatically discount the rooms according to your rate rules. A better per-night rate for a longer stay will help you stay competitive in the industry!\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-693039\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/oceanica-pricing-variables.png\\\" alt=\\\"oceanica-pricing-variables\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Variable Pricing<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe accommodation price can be changed automatically based on a number of guests. You simply need to add a needed number of the per-guest price variables that will be different from the base accommodation price.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour guests will see a relative price once they input their search parameters.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full wp-image-585240\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2016\\/12\\/booking-ical_support.png\\\" alt=\\\"motopress hotel booking plugin for wordpress\\\" width=\\\"467\\\" height=\\\"314\\\" \\/>Channel Manager for Bookings<\\/h3>\\r\\nSynchronize all reservations submitted directly on your site with those on OTAs like Airbnb. The system supports iCal sync, which means you can exchange bookings data with the channels where your property is listed and avoid overbooking.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe synchronization is possible only with those OTAs that support iCal file format (the most popular ones do.)\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-536104\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/06\\/oceanica-dock-and-support.png\\\" alt=\\\"documentation and support for wordpress themes\\\" width=\\\"460\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/>Docs and Support<\\/h3>\\r\\nIf you stuck somewhere, don\\u2019t worry - we are ready to help you in any preferable way!\\r\\n\\r\\nThe step-by-step guide of working with the theme, emails, chat, tickets. Just let us know when you run into any issue.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"A handcrafted Hotel WordPress theme for different hotel establishments: villas, vacation rentals, apartments, hostels and similar. Oceanica is your awesome hotel presentation with WordPress accommodation booking system built in \\u2013 all you need to maintain your online hospitality business like a pro.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/oceanica_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 844,\n                        \"name\": \"Hotel and Property Rental WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"hotel-rental-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 844,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Vacation rental WordPress themes and Hotel themes with the built-in WordPress Hotel Booking plugin by MotoPress included for free.\\r\\n\\r\\nThese property rental WordPress themes will definitely help you display the facilities and advantages of your single property website, small family hotel, elite boutique, hostel or cosy apartment for rent. Each template is beautifully designed, well-structured and equipped with easy booking tool - WordPress Booking plugin. \\r\\n\\r\\nMotoPress WordPress reservation plugin offers easy property management system, an iCal channel manager for OTAs, built-in payment gateways, offline and online payments, availability calendar, extra services, booking calendar, custom rates, seasonal pricing, taxes & fees, discount coupons and much more.\\r\\n\\r\\nUse this perfect combo of Hotel Booking Plugin and WordPress real estate theme and build your successful business with MotoPress\\r\\n\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 7,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"59.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.7.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 439687,\n                \"slug\": \"restaurant-menu-cart\",\n                \"title\": \"Restaurant Menu Cart\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2016-12-22 08:42:50\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-02-22 09:10:48\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=439687\",\n                \"content\": \"This plugin installs a shopping cart button in the navigation bar.\\r\\n\\r\\nPlugin options:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Display