e=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nLemongrass\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"46.5\\\" pos_y=\\\"61.5\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"right\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nScissors\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"41\\\" pos_y=\\\"86\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"bottom\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nMutton liver\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"7.26\\\" pos_y=\\\"48.5\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nSpoon\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"64.87\\\" pos_y=\\\"90\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"bottom\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nGinger\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_image_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Installation<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n<li>Go to Plugins &gt; Add New in your WordPress DashBoard<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Click Upload Plugin, Browse and Choose File, then select ZIP file of Image Hostspot plugin. <\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Click Install Now.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Click Activate to add new widgets right away.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Launch MotoPress Content Editor on any Page, Post or Custom Post Type<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Check Media group of objects to find new widget \\u2013 Image Hotspot<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>How to add Image Hotspot Widget<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n1. Drag Hotspot Image to the page and drop it there\\r\\n2. Select an image to add pointers to\\r\\n3. Set up an Inherit hotspot and tooltip theme that would be applied by default:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>hotspot color: custom, red grey, black<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>hotspot size: small, middle and large<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>tooltip theme: select predefined one or modify custom one with color picker<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>select tooltip position<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>define when the tooltip should be displayed: on hover, on click or always<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>How to add new hotspot to the image<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n1. Add new hotspot and it will appear at the center of the image\\r\\n2. Type tooltip text in the description field\\r\\n3. When you hover over the image you can see the x and y percentage position of the cursor at he top right hand corner\\r\\n4. Just put a cursor to the place where you want to add a pointer, remember the position percents and type them to X and Y Position fields\\r\\n5. Once you indicate the coordinates for a hotspot it will move to its place.\\r\\n6. You can also customize each hotspot individually if you do not want to use Inherit style\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_image_hotspot img=\\\"217503\\\" common_hotspot_color=\\\"mp-text-color-red\\\" common_hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" common_plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" common_hotspot_size=\\\"normal\\\" common_tip_theme=\\\"tooltipster-shadow\\\" common_custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" common_custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" common_tip_position=\\\"top\\\" common_tip_show=\\\"hover\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"30.62\\\" pos_y=\\\"34.9\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"mp-text-color-black\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"tooltipster-default\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nSome rest to digress from workflow\\r\\n\\r\\nand find an inspiration\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"33\\\" pos_y=\\\"66\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"custom\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#46a9f5\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"tooltipster-light\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"left\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nStay in touch with my\\r\\n\\r\\ncustomers and partners\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"65\\\" pos_y=\\\"86\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"custom\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#5dab49\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"custom\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#f6e2b0\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#474747\\\" tip_position=\\\"left\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nQuick notes when I\'m out of computer\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"85\\\" pos_y=\\\"70\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nA pen to make a quick notes\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"58\\\" pos_y=\\\"6.60\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"custom\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#fbcf1c\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"tooltipster-dark\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nMy laptop for typing posts, articles, reviews, etc.\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_image_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\nIt\\u2019s all about your imagination. Don\\u2019t miss your chance to make your WordPress blog unique with Image Hotspot widget.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Animated pointers for the images of your WordPress website - the extension of the MotoPress Content Editor. Create custom hotspots to make your images more informative and interactive. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/image_hotspot_addon.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 721,\n                        \"name\": \"Content Editor Addons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"content-editor-addons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 721,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Need an ultimate WordPress Page Builder toolkit without looking for solutions from different providers? Your one-stop solution is here - enhance your MotoPress Content Editor with a variety of these useful addons.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 7,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 700,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 700,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Free and premium WordPress plugins for your website. We ensure you get products created according to WordPress coding standards, niche-focused functionality and overall customization flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"10.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.4.1\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 191275,\n                \"slug\": \"countdown-addon\",\n                \"title\": \"Countdown Addon\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2015-11-09 10:34:44\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-06-21 11:42:06\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=191275\",\n                \"content\": \"Countdown Pro Addon is a new widget with advanced functionality for MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/content-editor\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Page Builder<\\/a>. Countdown timer is a great<strong> marketing solution<\\/strong> for your website. You may set a counter to track a discount duration, define the date of product release or website launch etc.\\r\\n\\r\\nAn intuitive interface allows you to create an eye-catching countdown timer visually with your mouse and without any line of code. You can drop the widget to any place of page or post, set the dates and time when counter should appear and disappear, entirely customize colors, and block sizes. It is fast and responsive so you might be sure it will look perfect on any screen.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Live Example<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_countdown_timer date=\\\"2021-12-31 23:59:59\\\" time_zone=\\\"server_time\\\" format=\\\"wdHMS\\\" shape_type=\\\"circle\\\" font_color=\\\"#1c7efe\\\" track_color=\\\"#1c7efe\\\" track_bg=\\\"#eee\\\" blocks_size=\\\"128\\\" track_width=\\\"6\\\" digits_font_size=\\\"32\\\" labels_font_size=\\\"11\\\" blocks_space=\\\"12\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Features<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>square and circular styles<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>custom colors for background, track and text<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>display content before the countdown starts<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>display content or redirect to an external URL when timer reaches zero<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>custom track and block size<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>fully customizable blocks<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Installation<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>go to Plugins &gt; Add New in your WordPress Dashboard<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>click Upload Plugin, Browse and Choose File, then select ZIP file of Countdown Pro Addon plugin. Click Install Now.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>click Activate to add new widgets right away.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>launch MotoPress Content Editor on any Page, Post or Custom Post Type<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>check Other group of objects to find new widget \\u2013  Countdown Pro<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>How to use Countdown Pro Widget<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>set the expiration date - the time at which the countdown expires<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>define a start date to show timer on this date. You can display custom text before this date.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>select a time zone between server time and visitor\\u2019s local one<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>set the format of countdown. Use \\u2018Y\\u2019 for years, \\u2018O\\u2019 for months, \\u2018W\\u2019 for weeks, \\u2018D\\u2019 for days, \\u2018H\\u2019 for hours, \\u2018M\\u2019 for minutes, \\u2018S\\u2019 for seconds. Upper-case characters for required fields and lower-case characters for display only if non-zero.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>define the style for timer between Default (square) and Circular<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>customize the following colors with color picker:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>background color<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>text color<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>track color<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>modify the blocks of counter to fit your needs within the following properties:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>track background color<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>block size<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>track width<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>digit size<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>text size<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>spacing between the blocks<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>if you set a start date for your countdown you can also add some content before it starts. Note: the text will be displayed on the website preview only and not available in the builder.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>you can also add custom content to appear when the countdown reaches zero.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>another option for expiration date is a redirect by URL. Since the counter reaches zero all the visitors will be redirected to any URL you wish.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\nOne of the main features is an option to add content before the timer starts and after it reaches zero. You can find it useful if you add a timer to count for a discount release and add coupon code to appear when it reaches zero. Moreover, you can enable automatic redirect to any URL after the counter is over. We are pretty sure you\\u2019ll find a way to apply the countdown on your WordPress site properly.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"A stylish countdown timer for promos, a product launch and other needs of your WordPress website. Customizable sizes and styles, setup and editing in several clicks.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/countdown_addon.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 721,\n                        \"name\": \"Content Editor Addons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"content-editor-addons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 721,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Need an ultimate WordPress Page Builder toolkit