h handier than default WordPress editor as it will help you build a multifunctional website totally visually. The theme is fully compatible with <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/wordpress-slider\\/\\\">WordPress Slider<\\/a>.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/profit\\/profit-shift-hide-frontpage-sections.png\\\" alt=\\\"Shift or hide front page sections\\\" \\/>Shift or Hide Front Page Sections<\\/h3>\\r\\nGet more freedom for the front page customization.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou can change the positions of any content block or entirely hide the unneeded ones. All the tweaks are made manually without technical help.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Profit WordPress Financial theme is perfect for accounting companies, brokers, financial consulting, insurance services, cryptocurrency, etc. Profit features widgets for financial sector, fully customizable header slider with 3 layouts, and lots of content modules to present your business.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/profit_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 18,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            }