\" link=\\\"#\\\" target=\\\"false\\\" align=\\\"left\\\"]\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\nAs result you will get such changes:\\r\\n\\r\\n[mp_grid_gallery ids=\\\"126540,126533,126535,126536\\\" columns=\\\"4\\\" size=\\\"large\\\" link_type=\\\"lightbox\\\" target=\\\"false\\\" caption=\\\"false\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Theme integration<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\nYou can also integrate MotoPress White Label plugin to any theme without installing the plugin. There is <strong>theme-sample.php<\\/strong> file included to the plugin package where you can manage the same re-branding settings by editing code. You should just follow these easy steps:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>download a class-tgm-plugin-activation.php file and copy it to a theme folder if you want to install plugins with a theme<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>copy MotoPressWhiteLabel.php to the theme folder<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>add code from a theme-sample.php file to functions.php one<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>configure \'default\' settings<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Re-brand MotoPress Content Editor, Slider and Content Editor addons using the White Label plugin and win over your clients with awesome website functionality! Rename MotoPress\\u2019 tools, change logos, icons and other info to use products as your own.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/white_lable_addon.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 721,\n                        \"name\": \"Content Editor Addons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"content-editor-addons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 721,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Need an ultimate WordPress Page Builder toolkit without looking for solutions from different providers? Your one-stop solution is here - enhance your MotoPress Content Editor 